Paper: hep-th/9307196

Date: 1993-07-31

Title: Free Field Representation For Massive Integrable Models

Authors: S.Lukyanov

Comments: 49 pages, RU-93-30

Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 167 (1995) 183-226

A new approach to massive integrable models is considered. It allows one tofind symmetry algebras which define spaces of local operators and to getgeneral integral representations for form-factors in the\ $ SU(2)$\ Thirringand Sine-Gordon models.